  "text": "Cloning 53BP1-mRuby. GFP-53BP1 plasmid was a generous gift from Jiri Lukas [CITATION_1] . This plasmid contains full-length mouse 53BP1 cDNA tagged with GFP. To visualize endogenously tagged p21-GFP and 53BP1 in the same cell line, we changed the GFP tag for an mRuby tag in the 53BP1 plasmid. We removed the GFP tag with BmtI and BspEI double digestion. We PCR amplified mRuby with following primers: forward 5 0 -gctagcatgaacagcctgatcaa-3 0 and reverse 5 0 -tccggaccctccgcccaggccggcga-3 0 . Digested mRuby PCR product was ligated into the cut 53BP1 vector and sequenced to check for in-frame ligation.",
